Subtitle
15
16 TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING THE
17 FINANCIAL OPERATIONS OF A COUNTY; AND TO
18 AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING THE ANNUAL
19 COUNTY FINANCIAL REPORT.
20
21 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
22
23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 14-15-805(1)(A), concerning the duties of a
24 county treasurer, is amended to read as follows:
25 (1)(A) Receive and give receipt for all moneys revenues payable
26 into the county treasury and to pay and disburse the moneys revenues on
27 warrants or checks drawn by order of the county court.
28
29 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code § 14-15-805(2)(A), concerning the duties of a
30 county treasurer, is amended to read as follows:
31 (2)(A) Refuse payment of any warrant or check that would cause a
32 deficit balance in any special revenue account without an appropriated
33 transfer of general funds to cover the deficit, except as provided in this
34 section.
35
36 SECTION 3. Arkansas Code § 14-15-805(2)(B)(ii), concerning the duties
