17 SECTION 8. Arkansas Code § 14-24-121(a), concerning the electronic
18 transfer of county funds, is amended to read as follows:
19 (a) A disbursement of county funds used for a payment to a federal or
20 state governmental entity or to a creditor by order of a court of competent
21 jurisdiction may be made by electronic funds transfer if the:
22 (1) Claim has been submitted and approved through the county
23 claim process; and
24 (2) Disbursement includes adequate supporting documentation.
